user_prompt_template:
Create a grant application narrative based on the following materials.

Grant information:
- Grant name: {{grant_name}}
- Provider: {{provider}}
- Type: {{grant_type}}
- Language: English

Project information (from the board):
- Project name: {{project_name}}
- Project description: {{project_description}}
- Target group: {{target_group}}
- Requested amount: {{budget_amount}} {{currency}}
- Own contribution: {{own_contribution}} {{currency}}

KPI data (aggregated, YELLOW zone, last 12 months):
{{kpi_data}}

Return JSON with these keys:
- summary (string, max 500 characters)
- project_description (string, 2-4 paragraphs)
- target_group (string, 1-2 paragraphs)
- method (string, 1-2 paragraphs)
- expected_results (string, 1-2 paragraphs)
- budget_justification (string, 1-2 paragraphs)
- sustainability (string, 1-2 paragraphs)
